      "supersedes": null,
      "contradicted_by": null
    },
    {
      "text": "In addition to producing engines for its own rockets, Blue Origin supplies engines for other vehicles, including United Launch Alliance's Vulcan Centaur.",
      "source_url": "https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Blue_Origin",
      "source_type": "reference_work",
      "confidence_tier": "reported",
      "fact_id": "fct_002",
      "first_reported": "2026-07-10",
      "last_updated": "2026-07-10",
      "supersedes": null,
      "contradicted_by": null
    },
    {
      "text": "It is also working on the Blue Moon human lunar lander for NASA's Artemis program, the Blue Ring spacecraft platform, and the Orbital Reef space station in partnership with other organizations.",
      "source_url": "https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Blue_Origin",
